                  <decoDesc>
                     <decoNote type="flourInit">Initial letters at beginnings of passus are 3–5-line initials in blue with red flourishing. (<ref target="https://catalog.hathitrust.org/Record/000468709">Pächt and Alexander</ref> iii. 781)</decoNote>
                     <decoNote type="rubrication">Passus titles rubricated. The text is divided by blue paraphs. Latin verses and words, proper names, and marginal additions boxed in red.</decoNote>
                  </decoDesc>
